    <svcsubsec>
        <title>ELECTRIC SHIFT UNIT</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>Text and illustrations provided by Eaton Corporation.</para>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
        <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
            <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
            <para>The electric shift unit motor is equipped with a worm gear set which operates a cam mechanism and a
                slider block to move a shift fork to shift the axle (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1400201">Figure 1</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1400201" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1400201" filename="../figg14/G1400201.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 1. Exploded View of Electric Shift Unit</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcproc>
